Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:32.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs42\fnNeon\shad0\c&HAB39E7&\pos(358,70)}Pootan{\fnArial\c&H181116&\b0} Autograph Session
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.03,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs18\fnNeon\shad0\c&HAB39E7&\move(549.462,117,535.301,117,0,1060)}Pootan{\fnArial\c&H181116&\b0} Autograph Session
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:36.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Pootan, I'm happy that I'll be able to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:40.99,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,350)}Gale Elementary School 5th Grade\NOsamu Kido (10)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}I've kept my eyes on Pootan since\Nthree years ago, when he wasn't famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since the content of the show\Nwas a little surreal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was worried if it was going\Nto be popular among children,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it seems like it took off successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:51.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Though I believed that they would be a hit,\NI'm overwhelmed with emotion by their success.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As a fan from when they were nobodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:57.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to see that they're popular,\Nbut I also feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:01.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs18\fnNeon\shad0\c&H972DD3&\bord3\frz7.535\3c&H85D5EE&\move(292.291,349,229.981,349,0,5010)}Pootan{\fnNeon\c&HDCE0D8&\b0\bord3\3c&H905041&\fs13}\N\N\N Autobiography
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And no matter how you look at these guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,there's no way that they know\Nhow funny Pootan really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:05.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I especially can't stand\N that punk with the afro hairdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no way that he knows\Nanything about Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:08.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But still, I should feel genuinely happy\Nnow that Pootan has become popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All I do is watch over you from the shadows.\NThat's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Your face shows more confidence now, Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't see the inexperienced look\Nthat you had when the show started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I remember you were hesitant about your timing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,as you hadn't gotten the hang\Nof the character yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay, please stay in line, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It'll be my turn soon. I'm a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is the first time that I'll see you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How do you do, Pootan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Somehow I feel something is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:45.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, they say that the actual looks\Nare different from TV images.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And I don't know much\N about those things either, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, he looks totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Besides, Pootan doesn't have\Na mustache like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:56.61,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs42\fnNeon\shad0\c&HAB39E7&\pos(358,13)}Pootan{\fnArial\c&H181116&\b0} Autograph Session
