Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:57.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs42\fnNeon\shad0\c&HAB39E7&\pos(358,76)}Pootan{\fnArial\c&H181116&\b0} Autograph Session
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs42\fnNeon\shad0\c&HAB39E7&\pos(358,76.5)}Pootan{\fnArial\c&H181116&\b0} Autograph Session
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's one thing to be a little different,\Nbut being this different is going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, why isn't anybody\Nmaking a big stink about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:06.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I see. Everyone is being\Ndeceived by that plush costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, they're transient fans, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As long as the person\N is wearing that plush costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they believe that it's Pootan,\Nno matter who's wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:17.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Pootan's also busy, so I'm sure there's times\Nthat he has to have a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:21.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a little annoying, but it'd be\N childish of me to get upset here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, then, I'll pretend that he's Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But he took off the costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:33.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, I see! He's Pootan, right?\NI'll acknowledge that he's Pootan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. He's Pootan and no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look, he's Pootan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The person who's signing is Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The person who's shaking\Nhands with me is Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:46.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And this is Pootan's autograph,\Nthat I've dreamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And who the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fnArial\frz279.5\pos(393.12,212)\c&H3E1731&\3c&HB68B9E&\bord0}OX Productions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The phones have been ringing\Noff the hook since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,with complaints about the autograph sessions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's why I said that you shouldn't ask\Na guy like that to be your substitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no point crying over spilled milk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Besides, yesterday we had autograph sessions\Nat twenty locations nationwide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:10.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But that's how it is when you're popular, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And there's a child in front of the office,\Nand he's making a big stink saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:17.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,he was deceived by a mustached guy\Nat yesterday's autograph session.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, then, I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Fine, then. Bring him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There was a mustached guy\Nat yesterday's autograph session.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, poo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:32.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You seem to be making\N some complaints about a mustache,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but as you can see, it was me\Nwho was at that site yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:38.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You see? I have the mustache too, poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But you don't usually\N wear mustache on TV, so why suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a joke, poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I feel that joke isn't very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:49.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now, if you understand, then hurry home, poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:53.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Was that really okay? You were\Ndealing with an innocent child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is how the world of show business works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Substitutes are everyday things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm somewhat kinder than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I know that, but I don't think\Nit's nice to deceive children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Guys who are amused\N by watching TV are all stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They aren't interested in the content.\NThey just like the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So they'll think that it's Pootan if we have\Nsomeone wear this plush costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who wears it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that means the case is closed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for another episode\Nof the popular show Pootan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My show got hijacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The audience was really cracking up again\Nat today's stage performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Your new performance style\Nseems to be a hit with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:35.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Usually a performance style is hard\Nto change once it takes root,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:38.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but you changed it splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:42.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, your performance style changed,\Nor rather everything has changed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You changed so much that it's like\Nyou're a totally different person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,or rather you're a different person...\Nor what should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're a different person, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This has become a real mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:51.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(180,0)\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(490.551,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:51.20,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\alpha80\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(453.165,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:51.24,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\alpha50\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(453.165,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:51.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\alpha20\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(453.165,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:51.41,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(413.513,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:51.53,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(374.994,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:51.66,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(336.475,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:51.78,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(295.69,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:51.91,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(256.038,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.03,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(216.386,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:52.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\c&H5DD5DD&\shad0\bord0.8\fnNeon\b0\pos(182.399,62)}Pootan{\fnArial\b1}\N in street clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\c&H0F1113&\bord0\frx12\fry348\frz3.797\move(282.095,129,347.804,88,0,1428)}Pootan - Popularity Rises\NHighest Rating 80%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:55.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That mustached part-timer took my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnAdobe Gothic Std B\c&H73BAC6&\bord1\fs46\frz14.187\move(476.956,133,391.987,173,0,1501)}Weekly TV
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnAnna\bord0\fs46\frz15.612\c&H5342C4&\b0\move(348.937,190,261.703,232,0,1501)}yen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord0\fnAdobe Gothic Std B\fs46\frz15.612\c&H6E3433&\fs26\move(642.361,98,557.392,140,0,1501)}Special Article{\c&HAF3BE7&\bord0\fs40}\N "Pootan"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnAnna\bord0\fs26\c&H0B140E&\frz17.114\move(346.671,257,259.437,297.5,0,1501)}New Series?!\NComplete Check
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My partner should have noticed the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have to get there quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fnArial\frz279.5\pos(393.12,212)\c&H3E1731&\3c&HB68B9E&\bord0}OX Productions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That mustached guy is a fake!\NI'm the real Pootan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll make a snappy comeback,\Nso you'll have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're rehearsing a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop it! He's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good job. You can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll start at two tomorrow, so come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey... What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Enough with your bad jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:27.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since there's a new Pootan, I'll say this now.\NI didn't like you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll be working with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if you accept such a thing,\Nthe public won't accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:39.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The public? The public has already\Naccepted him as Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's got an even better reputation\Nthan the previous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:46.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't it the case that you think you're\Nmore important than you really are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, in short, it doesn't matter\Nwho does Pootan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,His pay is cheaper than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:58.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If his popularity remains the same,\Nthe TV station will be happy to use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But he's quiet, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, he's more than just quiet.\NHe doesn't speak at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A surreal performance style\Nthat tries to be different
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,will find some brief popularity\Nwith the viewers, sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it won't last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:12.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the end, Pootan doesn't work without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you're that confident,\Nwhy don't you go it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:21.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or are you saying that you can't do anything\Nwithout Pootan's name and plush costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Don't get carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're an eyesore. Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? What are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The show's already on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The show?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But we're both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:37.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for another episode\Nof the popular show Pootan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:40.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's with you, Freddie?!\NWhat are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We were both replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.65,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,350)}Destrade High School Year 1 Boss\NNoboru Yamaguchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:48.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Pootan's plush costume, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why the hell is he in the middle of town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Moreover, I've seen that\Nmustached face somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've become a fan lately.\NI went to his autograph session too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:03.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, you. Would you let me\Nfeel that plush costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Are you trying\Nto pick a fight with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's Pootan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:13.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you think I'm just a funny youngster,\Nyou're in for some pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Say something, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's good to feel this\Nkind of tension once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a big mistake to think\NI'm always doing comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that. That guy\Nis talking to a plush animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's funny. Let's watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Crap... I'm trying to be serious,\Nbut I made people laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:35.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It seems that I was born with comic talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:37.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:41.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, what are you doing, bothering everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You should take off that\Nplush costume right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second. What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:51.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually, for various reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.30,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Various reasons = the story so far
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}I was hoping that Freddie'd return\Nat least the plush costume to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now return it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Does he still resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:04.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think you're partially\N responsible for what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:04.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's a pure man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:12.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He probably got into Pootan's role\Nas a result of fulfilling his duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Didn't this happen because\Nyou cut corners on your job
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,by using a substitute at the autograph session?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:21.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Indeed, you may be right, but\Nwhat more do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The answer is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the end, he's the fake one\Nand you're the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you show the difference clearly, he'll withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please show something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to do\Na quick performance here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're a pro comedian, right?\NThere must be something you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I don't have any\N quick gags that I can do, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Back when you debuted\Nand weren't yet popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,you were doing quick gags, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But they weren't popular at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since you came up against the wall of comedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,you switched to the plush animal\N performance of Pootan and succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? You remember that?\NI've already forgotten that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it like this?\NPut your hand on your forehead and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please stop it. I'm embarrassed\Njust remembering it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:05.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. You want to put that past behind you.\NI understand that mentality very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:09.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you're embarrassed about such a thing,\Nit's as if we can see your end as a comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look. You're at a crucial moment right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:17.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,where the important position of Pootan\Nmay be taken away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't feel that you're fighting fiercely for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try once with the mindset\Nyou had when you started?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:27.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Having a mind that doesn't fear shame\Nshould bring you one step up as a comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:33.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll return to the past\Nand show that performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:35.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You'll really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You guys, prepare to laugh. Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's 37.5 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's already taken it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I bet he got bored, since\Nwe kept going on and on.
