Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no need to say this now, but I'm asking\Nyou not to think this is the end of the show
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and to watch till the ending title scene after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Pootan is told that he looks\N handsome from behind too, poo.
